  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You flourish the weapon used in the casting and then vanish to strike like the wind. Choose up to five creatures you can see within range. Make a melee spell attack against each target. On a hit, a target takes 6d10 Force damage.</p><p>You then teleport to an unoccupied space you can see within 5 feet of one of the targets.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> The damage increases by 1d10 for each spell slot level above 5.</p><p>If you use a spell slot level of 9+, the damage is further increased by your weapon used and the weapon's properties.</p>",
